strings: <voice_0x01000E8F><se_def>The prince Carlos: I don't understand why my father didn't accept my decision and played me dumb.
<voice_0x01000E90><se_def>The prince Carlos: To expect him to catch so many lizards is dishonest.
<voice_0x01000E91><se_def>The prince Carlos: Hey... lizard! Just the name gave me goosebumps! I think the world would be better off without him.
<voice_0x01000E92><se_def>The prince Carlos: I saw a photo of the Princess Medea. It looks like a peach! If possible, I'll marry her tomorrow.
<voice_0x01000E93><se_def>The prince Carlos: But first you have to complete this difficult introductory course...
<voice_0x01000E94><se_def>The prince Carlos: I can't! skinny! At this rate I cannot marry Princess Mediah...
<voice_0x01000E95><se_def>The prince Carlos: bursting pain! Why am I such an unlucky prince? ....
<voice_0x01000E96><se_def>The prince Carlos: If I were in the low ranks I wouldn't care about this shitshow, oh I can't stand this dangerous lizard!
<voice_0x01000E97><se_def>The prince Carlos: But I never thought that if I were humble I would be able to marry a rare beauty like Princess Medea... Oh, how hard life is!
<voice_0x01000E99><se_def>The prince Carlos: I have some ideas
<voice_0x01000E9A><se_def>The prince Carlos: The sound you make when you're sick!
<voice_0x01000E9C><se_def>The prince Carlos: feel like vomiting! Chameleon move, what do you think he's doing here?
